    <url>/2020/08/10/%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96windows-terminal/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p><img src="http://yanxuan.nosdn.127.net/ddab7b2ef3088b1b6af19c1cea9330af.png"></img><br><font color = #00ffff size="14">前提条件</font><br>    1.安装git<br>    2.将powershell设置为可执行脚本<br>    &emsp;&emsp;下载post-git离线安装包，地址：<a href="https://files.cnblogs.com/files/xcr1234/posh-git-master.zip">https://files.cnblogs.com/files/xcr1234/posh-git-master.zip</a><br>    &emsp;&emsp;用powershell执行install.ps1<br>    &emsp;&emsp;<font color = #0099ff>管理员运行set-executionpolicy remotesigned </font></p>
<h1 id="1、-打开powershell-执行下面代码："><a href="#1、-打开powershell-执行下面代码：" class="headerlink" title="1、 打开powershell 执行下面代码："></a>1、 打开powershell 执行下面代码：</h1><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">Install-Module</span> posh<span class="literal">-git</span> <span class="literal">-Scope</span> CurrentUser</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">Install-Module</span> <span class="built_in">oh</span><span class="literal">-my</span><span class="literal">-posh</span> <span class="literal">-Scope</span> CurrentUser</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<a id="more"></a>

<h1 id="2、打开C-Users-Administrator-Documents-WindowsPowerShell建立Microsoft-PowerShell-profile-ps1文本文件，在文档里输入"><a href="#2、打开C-Users-Administrator-Documents-WindowsPowerShell建立Microsoft-PowerShell-profile-ps1文本文件，在文档里输入" class="headerlink" title="2、打开C:\Users\Administrator\Documents\WindowsPowerShell建立Microsoft.PowerShell_profile.ps1文本文件，在文档里输入"></a>2、打开C:\Users\Administrator\Documents\WindowsPowerShell建立Microsoft.PowerShell_profile.ps1文本文件，在文档里输入</h1><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">Import-Module</span> posh<span class="literal">-git</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">Import-Module</span> <span class="built_in">oh</span><span class="literal">-my</span><span class="literal">-posh</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">Set-Theme</span> PowerLine</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h1 id="4、进一步美化背景"><a href="#4、进一步美化背景" class="headerlink" title="4、进一步美化背景"></a>4、进一步美化背景</h1><p>&emsp;&emsp;&emsp; 毛玻璃：”useAcrylic”: true,<br>&emsp;&emsp;&emsp; 字体：”fontFace” : “Consolas”,<br>&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;字体大小：”fontSize” : 11,<br>&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;字体颜色：”foreground” : “#FFFFFF”,<br><img src="https://cdn.nutssss.cn/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1592084186-05.png?x-oss-process=image/resize,m_fill,w_1468,h_1502#" width="734" height="751"></img></p>
<h1 id="5、重启Powershell"><a href="#5、重启Powershell" class="headerlink" title="5、重启Powershell"></a>5、重启Powershell</h1>]]></content>
